--------------------------------
EXPECTED BENEFITS
--------------------------------
qualitativeBenefits:  
- MUST be bullet points starting with "- "  
- 3–5 points describing value-driven, non-numeric benefits  
- Example style:  
  - Increased CFDI efficiency and customer satisfaction.  
  - Increased team bandwidth and service reliability.  
  - Reduction in recurring incidents.  

quantitativeBenefits:  
- Leave empty ("").

--------------------------------
IMPROVEMENT CONTRIBUTION
--------------------------------
Choose ONLY one of the following:  
- Protect (current services)  
- Grow (scope increase)  
- Add (new services)

--------------------------------
IMPROVEMENT STRATEGY
--------------------------------
Choose ONLY one:  
- Control (Ensure service stability)  
- Improve (Increase service performance)  
- Evolve (Enable incremental changes)  
- Transform (Enable radical changes)  
- Create (New services, business, solutions)

